---
import '../styles/components/about-hero.css';
---

<section class="about-hero" id="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero__container">
    <h1 class="about-hero__title" data-animate="fade-up">
      We translate <span>Our Clients Dreams Into Reality</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="about-hero__text" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.2">
      We founded and developed Tenomad with all the aspirations of youth... Tenomad means 'Digital Nomad' – that is the spirit of dare to think, dare to do, not afraid challenges and difficulties of youth...
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
